## 13. 🏭 Factory Pattern para crear comida

**Cuándo:** "aplica un patrón de diseño" / "centraliza la creación"

```java
// NUEVA CLASE: FoodFactory.java
package com.mycompany.snakeexam2;

import java.util.Random;

public class FoodFactory {
    private static final Random random = new Random();

    public static Food create(Snake snake, SpecialFoodRemover remover) {
        int num = random.nextInt(6);
        switch (num) {
            case 0: return new SpecialFood(snake, remover);
            // case 1: return new PoisonFood(snake);  // si existe
            default: return new Food(snake);
        }
    }
}

// EN Board.java — reemplazar createFood()
public Food createFood() {
    return FoodFactory.create(snake, this);
}
